{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":72571,"originalJapaneseLine":"「総統閣下である俺が入ったら、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"When I, the Supreme Commander, enter,"},{"lineNumber":72572,"originalJapaneseLine":"　まずは俺様が中の連中に一発挨拶でかます。","translatedEnglishLine":"I’ll start by giving those inside a proper greeting."},{"lineNumber":72573,"originalJapaneseLine":"　お前は適当に盛り上げながら紙吹雪を散らせ」","translatedEnglishLine":"You, meanwhile, scatter the confetti to liven things up appropriately.\""},{"lineNumber":72574,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、昨日作っておけと","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, the confetti you told me to prepare yesterday"},{"lineNumber":72575,"originalJapaneseLine":"　仰っていた紙吹雪はこの為に……」","translatedEnglishLine":"is for this very reason…\""},{"lineNumber":72576,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……上手くいくでしょうか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Do you think this will go well?\""},{"lineNumber":72577,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それはお前次第だな。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That depends on you."},{"lineNumber":72578,"originalJapaneseLine":"　失敗したらしばく」","translatedEnglishLine":"If you fail, I’ll punish you.\""},{"lineNumber":72579,"originalJapaneseLine":"「まずお前が扉を開けて注目を浴びろ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"First, you open the door and attract attention."},{"lineNumber":72580,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そして、ランス総統閣下のおなーりー。これだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Then announce, 'The Supreme Commander Rance has arrived.' That’s it.\""},{"lineNumber":72581,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それじゃお殿様ですよ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well then, here comes the lord...\""},{"lineNumber":72582,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いいから早くしろ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Enough! Hurry up!\""},{"lineNumber":72583,"originalJapaneseLine":"「は、はいはい！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-yes, yes!\""},{"lineNumber":72584,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おはようございまーす」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good morning!\""},{"lineNumber":72585,"originalJapaneseLine":"そーっとシィルは総統司令部の扉を開けた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Sil quietly opened the door of the Supreme Commander’s headquarters."},{"lineNumber":72586,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おはようございます」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good morning.\""},{"lineNumber":72587,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おはようございます」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good morning.\""},{"lineNumber":72588,"originalJapaneseLine":"その場にいた兵士達はお愛想程度の挨拶をすると、","translatedEnglishLine":"The soldiers present gave polite greetings,"},{"lineNumber":72589,"originalJapaneseLine":"すぐに忙しそうに去って行った。","translatedEnglishLine":"then quickly left, looking busy."},{"lineNumber":72590,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ら、ランス総統閣下のおな〜り〜……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"T-The Supreme Commander Rance has ar-...\""},{"lineNumber":72591,"originalJapaneseLine":"シィルの声が聞こえていないのか、","translatedEnglishLine":"It was as if Sil’s voice wasn’t heard,"},{"lineNumber":72592,"originalJapaneseLine":"誰一人、顔すら向けなかった。","translatedEnglishLine":"not a single person even turned their face."},{"lineNumber":72593,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},{"lineNumber":72594,"originalJapaneseLine":"様子を窺っていたランスも","translatedEnglishLine":"Lance, who was observing, also"},{"lineNumber":72595,"originalJapaneseLine":"のっそりと姿を見せる。","translatedEnglishLine":"slowly showed himself."},{"lineNumber":72596,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あの……紙吹雪、どうしましょう……？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Um... what should we do with the confetti...?\""},{"lineNumber":72597,"originalJapaneseLine":"「どさー」","translatedEnglishLine":"*flurry*"},

{"lineNumber":72598,"originalJapaneseLine":"「きゃあああっ、服の中に入れないで下さいー。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Kyaaah, please don’t put it inside my clothes—"},{"lineNumber":72599,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ひう、チクチクしますー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"It’s prickly, ouch!\""},{"lineNumber":72600,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},{"lineNumber":72601,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……あ、う」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Ah, uh.\""},{"lineNumber":72602,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスとシィルが騒いでいても、","translatedEnglishLine":"Even though Rance and Sil were making a fuss,"},{"lineNumber":72603,"originalJapaneseLine":"注目するどころか、一瞥する者すらいなかった。","translatedEnglishLine":"not a single person paid attention, not even a glance."},

{"lineNumber":72604,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お、お前らなぁ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-You guys!\""},{"lineNumber":72605,"originalJapaneseLine":"　この総統閣下様々がわざわざ――！」","translatedEnglishLine":"The Supreme Commander himself went out of his way—!"},{"lineNumber":72606,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ら、ランス様、落ち着いて下さい。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"L-Lance-sama, please calm down."},{"lineNumber":72607,"originalJapaneseLine":"　皆さん、とっても忙しそうですし……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Everyone looks really busy…\""},{"lineNumber":72608,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お前のせいだ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It’s your fault!\""},{"lineNumber":72609,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あいたっ！？　ひんひん、すみません……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ouch!? Whimper, sorry...\""},{"lineNumber":72610,"originalJapaneseLine":"「皆、仕事に忙殺されて余裕がないんです。","translatedEnglishLine":"Everyone’s overwhelmed with work and has no leeway."},{"lineNumber":72611,"originalJapaneseLine":"　許してあげて下さい」","translatedEnglishLine":"Please forgive them.\""},{"lineNumber":72612,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おはようございます、ランスさん、シィルさん」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good morning, Rance, Sil.\""},{"lineNumber":72613,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお、ウルザちゃん」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, Ulza-chan.\""},{"lineNumber":72614,"originalJapaneseLine":"「忙しいというのは分かるが、しかしな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I understand being busy, but still…\""},{"lineNumber":72615,"originalJapaneseLine":"「今やここは世界中の情報が集まる中継地点です。","translatedEnglishLine":"This is now a relay point where information from around the world gathers."},{"lineNumber":72616,"originalJapaneseLine":"　仕事をいくらやっても片付かないんですよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"No matter how much work you do, it never gets finished.\""},{"lineNumber":72617,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……まあ、君がそこまで言うなら","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Well, if you insist that much,"},{"lineNumber":72618,"originalJapaneseLine":"　許してやらんこともなくはない」","translatedEnglishLine":"I suppose I can't not forgive them.\""},{"lineNumber":72619,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はい、ありがとうございます。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yes, thank you very much."},{"lineNumber":72620,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それでは早速ですが」","translatedEnglishLine":"Now then, without further ado,"},{"lineNumber":72621,"originalJapaneseLine":"ウルザはランスに書類の束を渡した。","translatedEnglishLine":"Ulza handed a stack of documents to Rance."},{"lineNumber":72622,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うむ、シィル。持っとけ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, Sil. Hold onto these.\""},{"lineNumber":72623,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスはそのままシィルに渡した。","translatedEnglishLine":"Rance passed them directly to Sil."},{"lineNumber":72624,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はい。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Understood."},{"lineNumber":72625,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あ、ランス様、作戦説明書のようですよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Ah, Rance-sama, it looks like these are operation briefing documents.\""},{"lineNumber":72626,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ほほう」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hoho.\""},{"lineNumber":72627,"originalJapaneseLine":"「では、反撃作戦を行うに当たって","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Then, as we carry out the counterattack operation,"},{"lineNumber":72628,"originalJapaneseLine":"　どうすればいいのか簡単に説明を始めますね」","translatedEnglishLine":"I’ll start with a simple explanation of what needs to be done.\""},{"lineNumber":72629,"originalJapaneseLine":"書類はシィルに手渡すと思っていたウルザは、","translatedEnglishLine":"Ulza, who had expected to hand the documents to Sil,"},{"lineNumber":72630,"originalJapaneseLine":"驚いた様子もなく淡々と説明を開始した。","translatedEnglishLine":"started the explanation calmly without any sign of surprise."}]}

